headline: NetApp Wins 2025 Google Cloud Infrastructure Modernization Partner of the Year for Storage
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., April 08, 2025--NetApp® (NASDAQ: NTAP), the intelligent data infrastructure company, today announced that it has received the 2025 Google Cloud Infrastructure Modernization Partner of the Year for Storage award.
